long_description: Our redesigned Big Eyes Pro Frog series provides the recreational and professional tournament angler with a superior alternative to the problems inherent with the double hook hollow body type frogs. Our Big Eye Pro Frog series now features a dual density PolyCore body, unique ProTec Weedguard (Patent#5,274,946) and a super sharp Owner hook. The high-density outer body and low-density inner core allow for longer casts and permanent flotation. Which means these frogs will never sink,or get waterlogged and will allow you increased contact and control when retrieving.
